paragraphs:
Types and formats of data generated or collected during the project:
Text (.docx, .doc, .txt, .pdf, .pptx). Papers, tutorials, reports and presentations less than 10 Gb;
Images (.fig, .png, .jpg, .eps .svg .pdf) no more than 10 Gb;
Software files (MATLAB (.m, .slx, .mat .mlx), Python (.py), Jupyter Notebook (.ipynb)). up to 10 Gb; 
Numerical files - generated database (.json, .csv, .xls, .xlsx, .mat), possibly over 200 Gb;

